    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "DATE: 10/2/61",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "At this time there appears to be no necessity for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "additional instructions for the field or insertion in the FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Handbook or Manuals relative to flying saucers.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Memorandum 9-30-60 pointed out that our policy",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "concerning unidentified flying objects is to conduct no",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "investigation but immediately refer facts to the Air Force",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "(Bureau Bulletin Number 57, 10-1-47); that SAC Letter Number",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "36, 3-29-49, reiterated this policy and set out data desired",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "by Air Force to be obtained when complaint received; that SAC",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Letter Number 43, 3-29-52, again pointed out our policy; that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Air Force on 11-12-57 assured that Bureau would be advised of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "any developments in this field of interest to us; and that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "there appeared to be no necessity for further instructions to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "field or insertion in agents' Handbook or Manual of Instructions",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "of our policy relating to flying saucers.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "During the past 12 months only one complaint regarding",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "flying saucers has been received. The facts in this complaint",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "were immediately referred to the Air Force.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
